<H1>Using a long listing</H1>

<P>To get more information about each file and directory,
use the command:</P>

<PRE WIDTH=80>   <STRONG>ls -l</STRONG>
</PRE>

<P>This gives you a long listing about each file and
directory, giving information about its:</P>

<OL>
<LI>access permissions</LI>
<LI>number of links</LI>
<LI>owner</LI>
<LI>group ownership (on BSD systems only seen with <SAMP>-g</SAMP> option)</LI>
<LI>size</LI>
<LI>date and time last modified</LI>
</OL>


